<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cut-down">cut down</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>砍倒：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Deserts are also created because people cut down trees and dig up grass.
人们伐树掘草，也会造成土壤沙化。</p><footer>外研③ – 4</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>减少；缩减</strong></h4>
<p>to reduce the amount of sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The car industry cut down production.
汽车制造商减少了产量。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you want to lose weight you have to <strong>cut down on</strong> fatty foods.
如果你想减肥就得少吃高脂食物。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We need to <strong>cut</strong> the article <strong>down to</strong> 1,000 words.
我们需要把这篇文章缩减至1000词。</p></div></div>